{"tid":2266781,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"諸朋好友","createTime":"2020-11-01T14:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T14:36:27.000Z","uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf06e976053bf33a2d31bf10ced583bf5f6915a8","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"諸朋好友[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n姜皓文(黑哥)於1986年藉參選友台電視先生加入演藝圈，原來他亦曾有擔任臨時演員的過去。黑哥入行後多做綜藝節目而少拍劇，聽聞與他「直率得罪」幕後有關，還試過連監製都敢呼喝！坐鎮友台多年的黑哥笑言電視生涯從未被挖角，也沒主動爭取機會離開娘家，後來卻遇上向製作單位大力推薦他的貴人，這人是誰？近年不少港產片都看到黑哥的蹤影，他還參演了TVB的重頭劇，可渴望當影帝或視帝？但得獎卻同時會為他帶來恐懼及壓力？"},{"pid":"e792cb2f3bcfa39f42876f06dbc860c46d3191ea","tid":2266781,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CCTVB 不了</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"61ec1f1fa026f32a2e2178a1b3c2c86638812073","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"秀文"},{"pid":"9dbfccfab6eca6d9e1ea1ca3d3a315638ea893ea","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e792cb2f3bcfa39f42876f06dbc860c46d3191ea","tid":2266781,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CCTVB 不了</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚3 概sosim搶曬smt生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1405924c5756865859f042908a11476e77f32540","tid":2266781,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9dbfccfab6eca6d9e1ea1ca3d3a315638ea893ea","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e792cb2f3bcfa39f42876f06dbc860c46d3191ea","tid":2266781,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CCTVB 不了<