 />\n<br />\n藝訓班是演藝界的搖籃，黃日華於四十年前「被報名」，甚麼原因令他首輪面試便被取錄，再與苗僑偉(三哥)成為好同學？二人分享藝訓班點滴，還笑言劉德華、梁朝偉的成就，均源於為表演練習時的出錯！<br />\n<br />\n不少圈中人會互相扶持，黃日華直指名堂響亮要靠幾位伯樂，他卻同時是張兆輝、郭富城的恩人？<br />\n<br />\n被問起二人可曾有爭執，華哥稱讚三哥是領頭人，總有辦法說服別人，令拗撬無從開展！華哥早前經歷喪妻之痛，三哥的窩心舉動更令他感動非常"},{"pid":"f1438613e397086d816545f04b03b395e40397f2","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"土"},{"pid":"7cccd2071b046d50ae7cbc8d4e94a4ef9ace7bfa","tid":2266781,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"張秀文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a1561fd00cc7f13d8841c15a458b29f8d82fd1","tid":2266781,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"2條pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50e96b3ce47c12e1ce905c699d8311dc4fb7f92","tid":2266781,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c821b45c04a7c82893e49982f4677651f858b9f","tid":2266781,"uid":141962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"比想像中好睇好多"},{"pid":"405e73c719b280ee1c5118e4cc7d0e2bcfabfcf9","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"諸朋好友[粵][PG]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n宣萱、歐陽震華(波比)可謂其中一對最佳螢幕拍檔，兩人緣份始於《壹號皇庭IV》，宣萱欣賞波比的真，波比卻「怪責」宣萱經常早到，還笑言是她的「錯」？交心朋友不介意互數優、缺點，而那些「缺點」亦非重要事。訪談過程中更發現崔建邦能夠討好波比，皆因一支百多元的「神棍」？波比藉藝訓班入行，因樣貌「突出」而試過一劇內化身多個小角色；但有一類角色，行內已知他不會再演。宣萱亦透露波比拍攝時最為介意出鏡的，竟是髮型"},{"pid":"71b5d725bc7308a5847a2865730cf86aaadb4e4f","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"messi打"},{"pid":"b5e9f52b17c0a1f5a2b96228857516f56b36d015","tid":2266781,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"揸你乳...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929da1cd734b78520c39dd0628e179684aeb83cd","tid":2266781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da0b22b3bd52ccad567484521c5aa9fc7d71936","tid":2266781,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"2個做得啦<br />\n叫崔健同秀文放工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass